Creative Commons CC0 1.0 Universal — Public Domain Dedication
=============================================================

Scope: this file covers the artwork/illustrations in this repository, namely
the images under assets/abcimg/ and assets/cat/. It does NOT cover the bundled
font (NotoSans-Bold.ttf), which is third-party and licensed under the SIL Open
Font License 1.1 — see assets/NotoSans-OFL.txt and the "Third-party assets"
section of README.md.

The illustrations were generated with OpenAI's ChatGPT. Purely AI-generated
images generally do not attract copyright protection, so rather than assert a
copyright license we could not reliably hold, the author dedicates them to the
public domain via CC0.

